{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0004", "text": "沿襲某些設定 但是我在懷疑", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 3, 4, 2, 2, 2, 5, 2, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyun4", "zaap6", "mau5", "se1", "cit3", "ding6", "daan6", "si6", "ngo5", "zoi6", "waai4", "ji4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "沿襲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "某些", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "設定", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懷疑", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0005", "text": "現代的新女性 另有氣質 祈求被鑑定", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 3, 3, 5, 4, 2, 5, 4, 3, 0, 0, 2, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jin6", "doi6", "dik1", "san1", "neoi5", "sing3", "ling6", "jau5", "hei3", "zat1", "kei4", "kau4", "bei6", "gaam3", "ding6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "現代", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "新", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "女性", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "另有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "氣質", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "祈求", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "被", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鑑定", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0006", "text": "唯有她 能夠珠光寶氣 不俗豔如落霞", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 3, 0, 4, 3, 3, 9, 4, 3, 2, 2, 0, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["wai4", "jau5", "taa1", "nang4", "gau3", "zyu1", "gwong1", "bou2", "hei3", "bat1", "zuk6", "jim6", "jyu4", "lok6", "haa4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "唯有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "珠光寶氣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "俗豔", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "落霞", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0007", "text": "就算穿得很樸素 仍難自棄高貴吧", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 3, 9, 4, 4, 0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zau6", "syun3", "cyun1", "dak1", "han2", "pok3", "sou3", "jing4", "naan4", "zi6", "hei3", "gou1", "gwai3", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "就算", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "穿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "樸素", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍難", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自棄", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高貴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0008", "text": "但是我知 今世我是我", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 5, 3, 3, 4, 5, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "si6", "ngo5", "zi1", "gam1", "sai3", "ngo5", "si6", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "今世", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0009", "text": "如何照抄 她的精美繡花", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "ho4", "ziu3", "caau1", "taa1", "dik1", "zing1", "mei5", "sau3", "faa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "照抄", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "精美", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "繡花", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0010", "text": "我都是假的 都不優雅", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 2, 9, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "dou1", "si6", "gaa2", "dik1", "dou1", "bat1", "jau1", "ngaa5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "假", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "優雅", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0011", "text": "由我去做其他吧", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 7}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 4, 2, 0, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jau4", "ngo5", "heoi3", "zou6", "kei4", "taa1", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "由", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "其他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0012", "text": "人有很多風格 不必一概似她", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 9, 3, 3, 4, 3, 3, 3, 4, 5, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jan4", "jau5", "han2", "do1", "fung1", "gaak3", "bat1", "bit1", "jat1", "koi3", "ci5", "taa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "人有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "風格", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一概", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "似", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0013", "text": "我的古怪與神化 仍然是我專有吧", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 9, 4, 5, 0, 4, 0, 0, 2, 5, 3, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "dik1", "gu2", "gwaai3", "jyu5", "san4", "faa3", "jing4", "jin4", "si6", "ngo5", "zyun1", "jau5", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "古怪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "與", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "神化", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍然", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "專有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0014", "text": "但是我知 風格要代價", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 5, 3, 3, 4, 4, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "si6", "ngo5", "zi1", "fung1", "gaak3", "jiu3", "doi6", "gaa3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "風格", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "代價", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "抱歉柯德莉夏萍", "artists": ["陳慧琳"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_5687", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NTY4Nw_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
